				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>The probable reason behind this wallpaper image compression is something to do with MEMORY USAGE. For slideshow intentions, mass-converting the wallpapers you want to use to BMP (and replacing their respective file extensions to JPG) is of great help.</p>
